# Lesarge Workforce Hub (WordPress workspace)

This private repository contains the WordPress workspace snapshot for the Lesarge Workforce Hub project.

Structure:
- wordpress-version/ (current WordPress installation snapshot)
- database/ (sanitized SQL dumps)
- documentation/ (architecture, migration plan)
- standalone-version/ (future PHP 8.2 MVC app skeleton)
- migration/ (migration scripts and notes)

IMPORTANT: wp-config.php, uploads, and other secrets are excluded by .gitignore.
